{"id": "art-212", "label": "Art. 212", "title": "Art. 212: Luarea măsurii controlului judiciar de către procuror", "slug": "art-212", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 212: Luarea m&#259;surii controlului judiciar de c&#259;tre\nprocuror </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_320956271\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2236\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_320956271\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Procurorul dispune citarea inculpatului aflat în stare\nde libertate sau aducerea inculpatului aflat în stare de re&#355;inere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_569731069\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2235\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_569731069\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Inculpatului prezent i se aduc la\ncuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;, de îndat&#259;, în limba pe care o în&#355;elege,\ninfrac&#355;iunea de care este suspectat &#351;i motivele lu&#259;rii\nm&#259;surii controlului judiciar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_445088941\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2234\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_445088941\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)M&#259;sura controlului judiciar poate fi luat&#259;\nnumai dup&#259; audierea inculpatului, în prezen&#355;a avocatului ales ori\nnumit din oficiu. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 209 alin. (6)-(9) se aplic&#259; în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2102322861\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2233\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2102322861\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Procurorul dispune luarea m&#259;surii controlului\njudiciar prin ordonan&#355;&#259; motivat&#259;, care se comunic&#259;\ninculpatului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}